<h2>Change in stools, Painful bowel movements and Worms in stool</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms change in stools, painful bowel movements and worms in stool including Dietary changes, Hemorrhoids, and Ascaris worms.</p>
<p>There  are 14 conditions  associated with change in stools, painful bowel movements and worms in stool. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
